## Third-Party Notices

This repository was originally based on work from:

- williamcorsel/hassio-addons

Parts of the structure, ideas and Home Assistant add-on patterns were inspired by or compared with:

- alexbelgium/hassio-addons
- itzg/docker-minecraft-bedrock-server
- poeggi/bds-ipv6fix
- Box64

The WinoMC IPv6 bind fix is implemented inside this repository and built from source as part of the WinoMC add-on image. The technical approach is inspired by the MIT-licensed `bds-ipv6fix` project by poeggi.

ARM64 / aarch64 support uses Box64 as a compatibility layer where required. Box64 is developed and licensed by its respective authors and is not owned by this project.

Minecraft, Minecraft Bedrock, Bedrock Dedicated Server, Mojang and Microsoft are trademarks or properties of their respective owners.

Home Assistant is a trademark or project of the Home Assistant community and its respective owners.

This project is not affiliated with, endorsed by, sponsored by or officially connected to Mojang, Microsoft, Home Assistant, itzg, poeggi, Box64 or the original upstream add-on repositories unless explicitly stated otherwise.